Class WiBeatCharacteristic

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.leantegra.wibeat.sdk.device.connection.WiBeatCharacteristic

  • public class WiBeatCharacteristic
extends Object
    Represents a Bluetooth GATT Characteristic of WiBeat.

    Contains a value and type of characteristic.
